<m0>Panthers sale won't affect arena<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .07 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   HEAD DEPTH TO THIS POINT IS .884 INCHES<m2><ql>
